{
  "slug": "configure-webhook-delivery",
  "title": "Configure Webhook Delivery",
  "description": "Set up real-time webhook notifications for squid run events",
  "category": "Delivery",
  "metadata": {
    "method": "POST",
    "endpoint": "/v1/delivery?squid={squid_hash}",
    "requiresAuth": true
  },
  "content": {
    "introduction": "Configure webhooks to receive real-time HTTP POST notifications when your squid's events occur. Subscribe to specific events like run start, completion, pause, or errors.\n\n{{RENDER:eventTypes}}\n\n## Webhook Payload\n\nLobstr sends a JSON payload to your webhook URL:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"id\": \"c39b1922a5424c3c84a7cb2ec731bc5f\",\n  \"object\": \"run\",\n  \"event\": \"run.done\",\n  \"squid\": {\n    \"id\": \"8177beb16fdf4e0e8d4b2ba767d1ffb5\",\n    \"name\": \"Google Maps Search Export (1)\"\n  },\n  \"timestamp\": \"2025/06/18 17:32:31\"\n}\n```\n\n{{RENDER:payloadFields}}\n\n## Retry Mechanism\n\nWhen `retry` is enabled:\n- Failed webhook deliveries are retried **up to 3 times**\n- Retries occur with a **15-minute delay** between attempts\n\n## Webhook Response Requirements\n\n- Your endpoint should respond within **30 seconds**\n- Return **HTTP 200, 201, or 202** to indicate successful receipt",
    "sections": {
      "eventTypes": {
        "title": "Event Types",
        "columns": [
          {
            "header": "Event",
            "key": "event"
          },
          {
            "header": "Description",
            "key": "description"
          },
          {
            "header": "Trigger Condition",
            "key": "trigger"
          }
        ],
        "rows": [
          {
            "event": "**run.running**",
            "description": "Run is actively executing",
            "trigger": "Emitted when a Squid run begins or resumes"
          },
          {
            "event": "**run.paused**",
            "description": "Run paused",
            "trigger": "Emitted when the run is temporarily halted (e.g., account limits reached)"
          },
          {
            "event": "**run.done**",
            "description": "Run completed successfully",
            "trigger": "Emitted when the run finishes without errors"
          },
          {
            "event": "**run.error**",
            "description": "Unexpected error occurred",
            "trigger": "When a run has crashed with an error"
          }
        ]
      },
      "payloadFields": {
        "title": "Payload Fields",
        "columns": [
          {
            "header": "Field",
            "key": "field"
          },
          {
            "header": "Type",
            "key": "type"
          },
          {
            "header": "Description",
            "key": "description"
          }
        ],
        "rows": [
          {
            "field": "**id**",
            "type": "string",
            "description": "Unique identifier for the run (hash)"
          },
          {
            "field": "**object**",
            "type": "string",
            "description": "Always \"run\""
          },
          {
            "field": "**event**",
            "type": "string",
            "description": "One of the subscribed Event Types"
          },
          {
            "field": "**squid.id**",
            "type": "string",
            "description": "Squid hash"
          },
          {
            "field": "**squid.name**",
            "type": "string",
            "description": "Human-friendly Squid name"
          },
          {
            "field": "**timestamp**",
            "type": "string",
            "description": "Event timestamp in YYYY/MM/DD HH:MM:SS format (UTC)"
          }
        ]
      },
      "bodyParameters": {
        "title": "Request Body",
        "parameters": [
          {
            "name": "webhook_fields.url",
            "type": "string",
            "required": true,
            "description": "Your webhook endpoint URL that will receive POST requests",
            "example": "\"https://your-webhook.com/endpoint\""
          },
          {
            "name": "webhook_fields.is_active",
            "type": "boolean",
            "required": true,
            "description": "Master switch to enable/disable webhooks",
            "example": "true"
          },
          {
            "name": "webhook_fields.retry",
            "type": "boolean",
            "required": true,
            "description": "Enable automatic retries for failed webhook deliveries (up to 3 attempts with 15-minute delays)",
            "example": "false"
          },
          {
            "name": "webhook_fields.events.run.running",
            "type": "boolean",
            "required": true,
            "description": "Subscribe to run start/resume events",
            "example": "true"
          },
          {
            "name": "webhook_fields.events.run.paused",
            "type": "boolean",
            "required": true,
            "description": "Subscribe to run pause events",
            "example": "false"
          },
          {
            "name": "webhook_fields.events.run.done",
            "type": "boolean",
            "required": true,
            "description": "Subscribe to run completion events",
            "example": "false"
          },
          {
            "name": "webhook_fields.events.run.error",
            "type": "boolean",
            "required": true,
            "description": "Subscribe to run error events",
            "example": "true"
          }
        ]
      },
